::Hot Rod::

Finally the time had come to prove himself to the people of this era, as
he had his Autobot brothers in the past.

He ran out in a fury, and fired two missiles at Dragonfly, to either
hurt or dissoriantate.

He follows up as he jumps through the air, attempting a round house kick
at Dragonfly's head.
